---
title: Easy Lamb Cottage Pie with Cheesy Cheddar Mashed Potatoes
description: This classic casserole combines saucy lamb filling and extra special cheesy cheddar mashed potatoes. Broiling for the last few minutes gives this cottage pie a delicious golden crust.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pate-chinois-sans-tracas-a-lagneau-6f1483e5.jpg
